jsx.ui.dd.event

Packages that use jsx.ui.dd.event
jsx.ui.dd Contains classes representing drag-and-drop related widgets. 
jsx.ui.dd.event Drag-and-drop event objects and their handlers. 
jsx.ui.vect.canvas For extra vector graphic widgets for interactive drawing based on 2d-canvas. 
jsx.ui.vect.draw For extra vector graphic widgets for interactive drawing based on SVG or VML. 
 

Classes in jsx.ui.dd.event used by jsx.ui.dd
DragMove
          A type of high level events that may be fired from a source widget when the browser mouse dragging-move event occurs on the element wrapped by the widget.
DragStart
          A type of high level events that may be fired from a source widget when the widget is being dragged.
DragStop
          A type of high level events that may be fired from a dragged widget when the mouse is released.
OnDragMove
          Declares an interface for high level event listeners that handle events of the DragMove type.
OnDragStart
          Declares an interface for high level event listeners that handle events of the DragStart type.
OnDragStop
          Declares an interface for high level event listeners that handle events of the DragStop type.
